com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.pois.helperclasses

Class PoisResponseOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.pois.helperclasses.PoisResponseOptions

  • public class PoisResponseOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Represent the response options, which are the request values passed to make the response. Buffer will be 0 if not encountered, and just the request field is guaranteed to be not null.
    Author:
    Marcos Henrique
